#### [MODIFY] [materials.css](file:///Users/l.poljakov/Documents/BMSTU/Development%20of%20internet%20applications/Development-of-Internet-Applications-Frontend/src/styles/pages/materials.css)

Добавить media queries:
- **768px**: уменьшить title до 32px, поиск в колонку (flex-direction: column)
